    <p>
		Aleph One is the open source continuation of Bungie's Marathon 2 FPS
		game engine. Aleph One plays Marathon, Marathon 2, Marathon Infinity,
		and 3rd-party content on a wide array of platforms, with (optional)
		OpenGL rendering, Internet play, Lua scripting, and more.
	</p>
	<p>
		Binary releases and scenario files are available at the Aleph One web site:
	</p>
